---
layout: default
title: Connecting the Dots Blog
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
socialSnippet: Showing how small efforts can cascade into big changes for our communities.
---

<div>
    <main class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-y-6 gap-x-12" x-data="{activeCategory: 'both'}">
        <header class="pt-8 space-y-4 col-span-full">
            <h1 class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-3xl leading-snug tracking-wide text-center font-display">
                <span class="text-hue">{{blogPage.blogName}}:</span> {{blogPage.introText}}
            </h1>
            <div class="max-w-md mx-auto prose text-center">
                <div class="leading-normal">{{blogPage.callForWriters | markdownify | safe }}</div>
            </div>
        </header>
        <aside class="top-0 hidden col-span-3 space-y-2 lg:block">

            <h2 class="pt-4 text-sm text-white text-opacity-75 border-t border-white border-opacity-25">Filter blog types:</h2>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
            {% for type in blogTypes %}
                <li class="text-sm">
                    <button
                        @click="activeCategory === '{{type}}' ? activeCategory = 'both' : activeCategory = '{{type}}'"
                        :class="{'text-hue text-opacity-100' : activeCategory == '{{type}}'}"
                        class="text-base tracking-wide text-white text-opacity-90 focus:ring hover:underline">
                        {{type}}
                    </button>
                </li>
            {% endfor %}
            </ul>
        </aside>
        <ul class="grid gap-y-6 lg:col-span-9 lg:gap-y-12">
            {% for item in collections.blog %}
                <li
                    :class="{'hidden' : activeCategory !== '{{item.data.tag}}' && activeCategory !== 'both'}, {'block' : activeCategory === '{{item.data.tag}}' || activeCategory === 'both'}" data-tag="{{item.data.tag}}">
                    {% include "components/_blog-card.njk" %}
                </li>
            {% endfor %}
        </ul>
    </main>
    {% include "components/_footer.njk" %}
<div>
